 😊 Smiley Face

A simple Smiley Face created using **HTML** and **CSS**. This project demonstrates how basic HTML 
elements and CSS properties can be combined to create shapes and illustrations without using images or graphics.

---

 🚀 Features

* Smiley face built entirely with HTML and CSS
* Uses CSS positioning and border-radius
* Responsive and lightweight design
* No external libraries or frameworks

---

 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3

---

