 📂 Project Structure

```text
Smiley-Face/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── README.md
└── images/
    └── smiley.png
```

---

▶️ How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open the project folder.
3. Open `index.html` in your preferred web browser.

---

 📚 What I Learned

* HTML page structure
* CSS positioning
* CSS `border-radius`
* Creating shapes with CSS
* Styling using colors and spacing

